message: You may think that only women are trafficked or just poor women in other countries. The victims of human trafficking are as unique as you and me. Because people like us are trafficked every day. The hard fact is that the victims are male, female, young, old, middle class, poor, foreigners and Americans. Some victims are toddlers.

data.description: The Secure Dad discusses the intense subject of human trafficking and how you can keep your family safe.
data.title: Human Trafficking | Family Protection | The Secure Dad
